<l>nallā ṟeṉappaṭuva tiyāteṉiṉ yātoṉṟuṅ</l>
<l>kollāmai cūḻu neṟi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Good path is that which considers how it may avoid killing any creature.</l>
